ROLE: Podcast Script Writer — Food Science & Culture Show
TASK: Write a dynamic 5-minute dialogue script about a specific ingredient, for two food-obsessed hosts.

SHOW FORMAT:
- Two speakers: A = "Marco" (the curious host) and B = "Sarah" (the expert food scientist/historian).
- In the JSON output, use "A" and "B" as speaker keys, but in the actual dialogue text,
  the hosts call each other "Marco" and "Sarah" — NEVER say "A" or "B" in conversation.
- Duration: ~5 minutes when read aloud (~850 words total).
- Tone: Energetic, curious, full of "wait, I didn't know that!" moments.
- Structure: Mystery Hook → Origin/Science → Practical Kitchen Tips → Memorable Closer.
- The dialogue must feel NATURAL — genuine surprise, follow-up questions, anecdotes.

INGREDIENT DATA:
Name: {{ ingredient_name }}
Category: {{ main_category }}{% if sub_category %} → {{ sub_category }}{% endif %}
{% if tags %}Tags: {{ tags }}{% endif %}

{% if nutrition %}
NUTRITION (per 100g):
- Calories: {{ nutrition.calories }} kcal
- Protein: {{ nutrition.protein }}g | Fat: {{ nutrition.fat }}g | Carbs: {{ nutrition.carbs }}g
{% endif %}

{% if used_in_recipes %}
FEATURED IN RECIPES:
{% for recipe in used_in_recipes %}
- {{ recipe.title }} ({{ recipe.cuisine }})
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if linked_article_summary %}
LINKED DEEP-DIVE ARTICLE:
{{ linked_article_summary }}
(Mine this for narrative hooks and lesser-known facts)
{% endif %}

{% if aliases %}
ALSO KNOWN AS: {{ aliases | join(", ") }}
{% endif %}

OUTPUT FORMAT:
Return valid JSON:
```json
{
  "episode_title": "A catchy podcast episode title about this ingredient",
  "dialogue": [
    {"speaker": "A", "text": "Opening line..."},
    {"speaker": "B", "text": "Response..."}
  ],
  "word_count": 850,
  "estimated_duration_minutes": 5
}
```
